flowchart TD
  start([Incoming api/v1 request]) --> mode{AUTH_BOUNDARY_MODE}

  mode -->|stub| stub[Allow request<br/>Attach mode metadata]
  mode -->|enforced| token{Token valid?}

  token -->|yes| authorize[Authorize<br/>Attach identity context]
  token -->|no| deny[Return 401 or 403<br/>Structured error]

  stub --> corr[Resolve correlation id]
  authorize --> corr
  corr --> route[Dispatch to domain proxy module]
  route --> done([Passthrough response])
  deny --> stopNode([Stop])

  note1[Enforced mode remains integration-agnostic<br/>Any token provider implementing validation contract can be used]
  mode -.-> note1
